{"id": "1482634904129900585", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "1106338057856229426", "author_name": "raw39", "author_bot": false, "content": "キーオーダー200回で覚醒体配るキャンペーンでどれ取ればいいかな？って話ですね", "timestamp": "2026-03-15T07:01:47.169000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["516998769888329749"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1482535359589122169", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1482635222825701539", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "私ならダフォダイルを取ります。", "timestamp": "2026-03-15T07:03:03.152000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1482635346717184061", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "サルバドル/カーシア/ダフォダイル/ファイントあたりで。", "timestamp": "2026-03-15T07:03:32.690000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1482636260383260783", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1106338057856229426", "author_name": "raw39", "author_bot": false, "content": "サルバドル軸は実際強いし攻略面良さそうには思います。あいにく持ってないので火力感等イメージがつきにくいので教えてもらえるとありがたいです", "timestamp": "2026-03-15T07:07:10.525000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1482636365844709549", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "||トゥルーは触手のダメージを伸ばせないとダメージ出しにくく、運命の札も3凸ないと火力が伸びないです。\nまた、3凸しないとコストが重すぎてまともに運用ができませんが、3凸をしてもほかの限定キャラの1凸とかと同じくらいのパワーのことが多いです。||", "timestamp": "2026-03-15T07:07:35.669000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1482636866091094016", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "599171149431046156", "author_name": "foxcatfurry", "author_bot": false, "content": "クリティカル！", "timestamp": "2026-03-15T07:09:34.937000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1482637545979248732", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "1106338057856229426", "author_name": "raw39", "author_bot": false, "content": "なるほど\nダフォダイルはやっぱり火力出ますか？", "timestamp": "2026-03-15T07:12:17.035000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1482636365844709549", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1482637736992178340", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "サルバドルは3凸で火力が跳ね上がるので、2凸までと3凸以降で分けて話します。\n2凸まではまぁそこそこの全体火力がある防御型という感じで、一人で火力を任せるのは厳しいです。防御面はめっちゃ硬いので、入れるだけで安定します。\n3凸以降は火力が跳ね上がり、サルバドルの2コスト連打とカーシアの軟化だけでボスが消し飛ぶくらいには火力高いです。\n最強です。", "timestamp": "2026-03-15T07:13:02.576000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1482636260383260783", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1482638129646276733", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "ダフォダイルはそこそこ火力出るという感じですが、真の強みは1コストの全体軟化とダメージ強化の獲得にあります。\n味方の火力補助もしながら自分も火力出せるという感じで、とても便利です。", "timestamp": "2026-03-15T07:14:36.192000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1482638229873365174", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "正直課金とか出来るのであれば、サルバドル3凸さえすればゲームクリアだと思います", "timestamp": "2026-03-15T07:15:00.088000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1482638256079245426", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1106338057856229426", "author_name": "raw39", "author_bot": false, "content": "3凸欲しいんですけども…揃うのいつになることやら…", "timestamp": "2026-03-15T07:15:06.336000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1482638477961990276", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "今からガチャ引くのであれば、個人的にはライカーモチーフ札>ライカー\nの順で引くのがおすすめです。\nライカーはデカいバフをかけられて、自分でもそこそこ火力を出せて強いです。", "timestamp": "2026-03-15T07:15:59.237000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1482638574133313650", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "ライカーイベントのSR札もめっちゃ強いのでお忘れなく！", "timestamp": "2026-03-15T07:16:22.166000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
